@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nxhcvc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.abs(tmp + 0.69)) / ((v2 + 0.48 - v0 + 0.07) - v1))
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.exp(tmp))
    v1 = tmp
    tmp = 0.01
    tmp = v1
    v0 = tmp
    v2 = ((0.37 + (v0 + 0.77 + v0 + 0.16)) / ((v2 + 0.04 - tmp + 0.47) - wp.cos(v0 + 0.69)))
    data[tid] = v0
